{
  "stem": "15028.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It started a hunger, till when-- took a little while, and then we got back to ourselves, the family.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The family, we got back with food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We start dealing more, opened up a little more to-- a-- do business in the-- by the Hungarians, under the Hungarian regime.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it started getting better.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father was dealing, back with the cattles, and with the lumber.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then that was in the wintertime.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the summertime, he used to lease out from the government.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He did it in-- but the Romanian he had to lease out mountains from the government, and the spring, by March.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then big mountains, few mountains, where you-- a lot of acres, and acres, and acres, and then he made a deal with the gentiles in every town.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, they wanted to work their land, and for the-- for the animals to have the hay, and have the potatoes, and have other things.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they-- the cattle, [INAUDIBLE], or the horses, or the cows, what gave milk, or the sheep, what they were milking, he couldn't keep them in the summertime, and do the work, and keep them, and feed them.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he didn't have the hay, neither.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Well, he had to grow it in the summertime and get it ready for the winter.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my-- my father, shall rest in peace, made deals.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Let's say if a-- if a gentile had 100 sheep, and he had 5-- 5 cows, and they gave milk, so he made a deal for the four months-- three, four months.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He should be able to work the land.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He paid him to keep, in pasture, all this cattles and-- and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he took it up in the-- in the mountains.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
